Package: python3-ps3iso
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, genisoimage
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11~), dh-python, python3-all, python3-setuptools, python-docutils, python-sphinx
X-Python3-Version: >= 3.6
Suggests: python-ps3iso-doc
Description: Playstation 3 image manager and PARAM.SFO reader (Python 3)
 This package contains the ps3iso tool and associated Python library 
 for managing existing Playstation 3 image files
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 3.

